SPC t 8 -- Highlight any character past the 80th column
SPC t f -- Display the fill column (by default the fill column is set to 80)
SPC t h h -- Toggle highlight of the current line
SPC t h i -- Toggle highlight indentation levels
SPC t h c -- Toggle highlight indentation current column
SPC t i -- Toggle indentation guide at point
SPC t l -- Toggle truncate lines
SPC t L -- Toggle visual lines
SPC t n -- Toggle line numbers
SPC t v -- Toggle smooth scrolling

SPC T ~ -- Display ~ in the fringe on empty lines
SPC T F -- Toggle frame fullscreen
SPC T f -- Toggle display of the fringe
SPC T m -- Toggle menu bar
SPC T M -- Toggle frame maximize
SPC T t -- Toggle tool bar
SPC T T -- Toggle frame transparency and enter transparency transient state
# Modeline
SPC t m b -- Toggle the battery status
SPC t m c -- Toggle the org task clock (available in org layer)
SPC t m m -- Toggle the minor mode lighters
SPC t m M -- Toggle the major mode
SPC t m n -- Toggle the cat! (if colors layer is declared in your dotfile)
SPC t m p -- Toggle the point character position
SPC t m t -- Toggle the mode line itself
SPC t m v -- Toggle the version control info
SPC t m V -- Toggle the new version lighter

# Minor Modes
SPC t - -- Centered-cursor mode
SPC t 8 -- Toggle highlight of characters for long lines
SPC t C-8 -- Global toggle highlight of characters for long lines
SPC t C-- -- Global centered cursor
SPC t a -- Auto-completion
SPC t c -- Camel case motion with subword mode
SPC t E e -- Emacs editing style (holy mode)
SPC t E h -- Hybrid editing style (hybrid mode)
SPC t f -- Fill-column-indicator mode
SPC t F -- Auto-fill mode
SPC t g -- Golden-ratio mode
SPC t h i -- Toggle highlight indentation levels
SPC t h c -- Toggle highlight indentation current column
SPC t i -- Indentation guide
SPC t C-i -- Global indentation guide
SPC t I -- Aggressive indent mode
SPC t K -- Which-key mode
SPC t p -- Smartparens mode
SPC t C-p -- Global smartparens
SPC t s -- Syntax checking (flycheck)
SPC t S -- Enabled in spell checking layer (flyspell)
SPC t w -- Whitespace mode
SPC t C-w -- Global whitespace
SPC t W -- Automatic whitespace cleanup (see dotspacemacs-whitespace-cleanup)
SPC t C-W -- Automatic whitespace cleanup globally
SPC t y -- Yasnippet mode